        <updateDate>2021-04-20T19:47:43Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Improving College Affordability for our Guard and Reserve Act</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes all members of the Armed Forces&mdash;including reservists or those in the National Guard and regardless of their duty status&mdash;to claim independent student status when applying for federal financial aid. Currently, active duty service members and veterans of the Armed Forces may claim such independent student status. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
